</title>
<subSubSection id="55252434E1E37AD99F72243F1FB7A36E" pageId="null" pageNumber="763" type="description">
<paragraph id="4EAB50441E8414FA086C0612E8D12FCF" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="30E4AFEED380247E11BB009E85B458CF" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Atriplex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="763" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hortensis">
<emphasis id="51B836BB4A08E58B2D07BC3E969540E9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">A. hortensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="25563A3E942B893D9145E3F1DC5F4756" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">
Auch 
<normalizedToken id="A6F7691E569B2D0BE57D2DBF4F4F9212" originalValue="ältere" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">aeltere</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="5F6C34D2AF61CC9B9569A554C5E90B80" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
unterseits grau bis 
<normalizedToken id="B5481CB4E08FE2831064AF9F08D21D4C" originalValue="weiβ" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">weiβ</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, oft grob und geschweift 
<normalizedToken id="05E7BB448B1BC89CFA729468696B5254" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
; 
<emphasis id="01A3F0CAD3648CE4C67F3930124EB1AA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">
<normalizedToken id="E8FC08A8BE18DC1548001EC751FF1502" originalValue="Vorblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">Vorblaetter</normalizedToken>
meist kleiner
</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken id="938A41137179D774899FA174116EF527" originalValue="größter" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">groesster</normalizedToken>
Durchmesser 5-10 mm) und deutlicher zugespitzt. - 
<normalizedToken id="9CE8AEFECC3627789DA4F19681292736" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer und Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AF02126EF05761442C36391DC94ECDC5" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">
<emphasis id="A476D18BF5EDE12D3AB0E83E319B513A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="28ECFB11F68F90A706A2323DC8418AEC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">18:</emphasis>
Ohne Herkunftsangabe des Materials (Wulff 1937).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9084E31207CDAA6CD638594507406ED8" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">
<emphasis id="DAE5A712882273AC4F25868E5973680B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="396CA8F657180D983C479254A9A84BFF" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Atriplex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="763" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hortensis">
<emphasis id="FB8DDA5B2E8FF69FA99B4D695754418A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">A. hortensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="776F843A58768F23E54A945605C43831" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">
<emphasis id="604810FF6960F98C43D7B25BBBE394EC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="FF0C416A7DB1F9F27CB260C3B3F089AF" originalValue="Ursprünglich" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">Urspruenglich</normalizedToken>
west- und zentralasiatische Pflanze;
</emphasis>
heute in 
<taxonomicName id="ED6E1EF0B4600DC813C4FD5C0BBF2547" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Europa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="763" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Europa</taxonomicName>
weit verbreitet. Verbreitungskarte von Meusel (1964). - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="464CF065478CD0478BBF69083F59896A" originalValue="Elsaß" pageId="null" pageNumber="763">Elsass</normalizedToken>
; in Ausbreitung begriffen.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
